data.description: This inviting condo is tucked away in a quiet gated community within walking distance to the beach. As you enter, you're greeted by a bright open floor plan with a great flow for entertaining and everyday living. The open kitchen offers granite countertops, white cabinetry, a breakfast bar, and ample cabinet and counter space. Refrigerator to convey, with an acceptable offer and as part of the sales contract. Enjoy your morning coffee from the screened-in porch located off of the family/great room. The spacious master bedroom features a tray ceiling, a walk-in closet, and a private en suite bathroom. You'll appreciate neighborhood amenities, including 6 community pools and hot tubs, 2 kiddie pools, tennis courts, a fitness center, a game room, charcoal and gas grills, picnic areas, walking trails, and bike paths. Also, golf carts are allowed in the community. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and the beach. Come see your new home, today!
